# ASSETS
| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-------------|----------|
| Images | `snake_case` | `baby_growth_week_20.png` |
| Icons | `snake_case` | `heart_icon.svg` |
| Animations | `snake_case` | `loading_indicator.json` |
| Fonts | `PascalCase` (folder) | `Poppins/`, `Roboto/` |
| Audio | `snake_case` | `notification_tone.mp3` |

Assets live under:  
`assets/images/`, `assets/icons/`, `assets/fonts/`, `assets/audio/`, `assets/lottie/`.

