# MARKDOWN / DOCS
| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-------------|----------|
| Docs | `kebab-case` | `system-design.md`, `data-model.md` |
| Guides | `kebab-case` | `feature-guide.md` |
| Policies | `kebab-case` | `privacy-policy.md` |

- Always use lowercase, hyphen-separated.
- Prefix specialized docs with their scope if needed:  
  e.g. `biomarkers-spec.md`, `ai-chat-overview.md`.

