# DATABASE / BACKEND FILES
| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-------------|----------|
| Migration files | `timestamp__table_name.sql` | `2025_01_10__create_user_table.sql` |
| SQL views / triggers | `snake_case.sql` | `user_summary_view.sql` |
| Drift files | `snake_case.drift` | `biomarker_tables.drift` |

- Keep migration names deterministic and ordered.
- Match table/entity names exactly with **data_model.md** definitions.

